<h1>Problem 2139 - 2013 Balkan MO, P3 of 4</h1>
<h2 class='difficulty'>Difficulty: 7</h2>
<p>Let \(S\) be the set of positive real numbers. Find all functions \(f\colon S^3 \to S\) such that, for all positive real numbers \(x\), \(y\), \(z\) and \(k\), the following three conditions are satisfied:</p>
<p>(a) \(xf(x,y,z) = zf(z,y,x)\),</p>
<p>(b) \(f(x, ky, k^2z) = kf(x,y,z)\),</p>
<p>(c) \(f(1, k, k+1) = k+1\).</p>
